---
description: Gate readiness rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Gate results must be `READY`, `READY_WITH_RISKS`, or `BLOCKED`.

Every gate check must list required evidence found, missing evidence, blockers,
non-blocking risks, and next actions.

If feature ID, release ID, owner, impacted systems, required docs, tests, or
approvals are unknown, do not mark the gate `READY`.
